{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"LocalizationErrorAttribute","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"LocalizationErrorAttribute","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"LocalizationErrorAttribute"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"SwiftErrorKit"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:13SwiftErrorKit012LocalizationB9AttributeV","symbolKind":"struct"},"abstract":[{"text":"An error attribute to provide a localized user message.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftErrorKit\/documentation\/SwiftErrorKit"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftErrorKit\/documentation\/SwiftErrorKit\/ErrorAttribute"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"LocalizationErrorAttribute","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It’s a kind of alternative to "},{"code":"LocalizedError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" which has some disadvantages:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"LocalizedError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" requires the localization values on initialization. This works ok"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for general messages, but can be limiting to provide more descriptive messages due to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"limited context.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It’s paradoxical that in a limited context, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LocalizedError"},{"type":"text","text":" has four properties which,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in my opinion, form an am